sentences: As a composer, he has received an ASCAP Jazz Composer Award, the 2008 and 2011 Chamber Music America New Works Grant, and the Victor Lynch-Staunton award by the Canada Council for the Arts.
From 2008 to 2015, he produced a multi-genre performance series at the Broad Stage in Santa Monica, California.
